query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ca.classical-analysis-and-odes',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'fa.functional-analysis',
'gr.group-theory',
'lie-groups',
'mg.metric-geometry',
'real-analysis');
